<em>展开全文</em>
</a>
</section>
</div>
<div class="hidden-content control-hide">
<p><strong>材料：鲜香菇6朵、娃娃菜300克、年糕200克、鸡汤</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20181128/4637ef494936446899330b4b5a0b9c07.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p><strong>制作：</strong></p>
<p>1.取一汤锅，舀入几勺子鸡汤，扯个鸡腿，还有香菇放在锅里。</p>
<p>然后将砂锅端到火火上煮开，加盐调味。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20181128/f83e36cde322432d92c50f8de8e730a0.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">2.然后将年糕下锅煮。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20181128/8b298bb0d6e24b2e9c934d0d4bd0bf9d.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">3.煮开后就可将娃娃菜头向下按入锅中，再煮开就可以享用了。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20181128/138aa44ea99a4acdbf7c8b258b7d38a8.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p><strong>细微小语：</strong></p>
<p>食材下锅的顺序要按照菜谱里说的做，因为年糕久煮就坨在一起了，而娃娃菜更是入锅就软了。</p>